sequenceDiagram
    participant Coordinator as MAP Coordinator
    participant A1 as Agent A1 (Planner)
    participant A2 as Agent A2 (Reviewer)

    Note over Coordinator: MAPSessionStarted
    Coordinator->>A1: Assign role: planner
    Coordinator->>A2: Assign role: reviewer
    Note over Coordinator: MAPRolesAssigned

    Note over Coordinator: Turn 1: Planner
    Coordinator->>A1: Dispatch token (Turn 1)
    Note over Coordinator: MAPTurnDispatched (A1)
    A1->>A1: Execute planning task
    A1->>Coordinator: Signal completion
    Note over Coordinator: MAPTurnCompleted (A1)

    Note over Coordinator: Turn 2: Reviewer
    Coordinator->>A2: Dispatch token (Turn 2)
    Note over Coordinator: MAPTurnDispatched (A2)
    A2->>A2: Execute review task
    A2->>Coordinator: Signal completion
    Note over Coordinator: MAPTurnCompleted (A2)

    Note over Coordinator: Turn 3: Planner (Revision)
    Coordinator->>A1: Dispatch token (Turn 3)
    Note over Coordinator: MAPTurnDispatched (A1)
    A1->>A1: Execute revision task
    A1->>Coordinator: Signal completion
    Note over Coordinator: MAPTurnCompleted (A1)

    Note over Coordinator: MAPSessionCompleted
